<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Welcome Email</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .header {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px 0;
            background-color: #007bff;
            color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0;
        }

        .content {
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #666666;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Welcome to Jobber!</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <p>Dear <%= userName %>,</p>
            <p>Welcome to Jobber! We're excited to have you on board.</p>
            <p>Thank you for joining us. If you have any questions, feel free to reach out.</p>
            <p>Best regards,<br>The Jobber Team</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>&copy; 2023 Jobber. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>